\par }{\insrsid7090824\charrsid536913 OK. A third cause of the heating process was compression due to gravity. As the size of the planet }{\insrsid7090824\charrsid4224902 grew}{\insrsid3627952\charrsid4224902  }{\insrsid7090824\charrsid536913 
